@startuml Sequence Diagram - Admin Xem Dashboard

actor Admin
participant "HomeController" as Controller
participant "ApplicationDbContext" as DbContext
participant "Database" as DB

Admin -> Controller: GET /Admin/Home/Index
Controller -> Controller: Tính toán DateTime (today, thisMonth, lastMonth)

== Thống kê tổng quan ==
Controller -> DbContext: CountAsync(Orders)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders
DB -> DbContext: TotalOrders
DbContext -> Controller: TotalOrders

Controller -> DbContext: SumAsync(Orders.Total)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT SUM(Total) FROM Orders
DB -> DbContext: TotalRevenue
DbContext -> Controller: TotalRevenue

Controller -> DbContext: CountAsync(Products)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Products
DB -> DbContext: TotalProducts
DbContext -> Controller: TotalProducts

Controller -> DbContext: CountAsync(Users)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Users
DB -> DbContext: TotalCustomers
DbContext -> Controller: TotalCustomers

== Thống kê hôm nay ==
Controller -> DbContext: Orders.Where(OrderDate.Date == today).CountAsync()
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders WHERE OrderDate = today
DB -> DbContext: TodayOrders
DbContext -> Controller: TodayOrders

Controller -> DbContext: Orders.Where(OrderDate.Date == today).SumAsync(Total)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT SUM(Total) FROM Orders WHERE OrderDate = today
DB -> DbContext: TodayRevenue
DbContext -> Controller: TodayRevenue

== Thống kê tháng này ==
Controller -> DbContext: Orders.Where(OrderDate >= thisMonth).CountAsync()
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders WHERE OrderDate >= thisMonth
DB -> DbContext: MonthOrders
DbContext -> Controller: MonthOrders

Controller -> DbContext: Orders.Where(OrderDate >= thisMonth).SumAsync(Total)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT SUM(Total) FROM Orders WHERE OrderDate >= thisMonth
DB -> DbContext: MonthRevenue
DbContext -> Controller: MonthRevenue

== Đơn hàng gần đây ==
Controller -> DbContext: Orders.Include(User).OrderByDescending(OrderDate).Take(10)
DbContext -> DB: SELECT TOP 10 Orders với User ORDER BY OrderDate DESC
DB -> DbContext: RecentOrders
DbContext -> Controller: RecentOrders

== Thống kê theo trạng thái ==
Controller -> DbContext: CountAsync(Orders.Where(Status == "Pending"))
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders WHERE Status = 'Pending'
DB -> DbContext: PendingOrders
DbContext -> Controller: PendingOrders

Controller -> DbContext: CountAsync(Orders.Where(Status == "Confirmed"))
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders WHERE Status = 'Confirmed'
DB -> DbContext: ConfirmedOrders
DbContext -> Controller: ConfirmedOrders

Controller -> DbContext: CountAsync(Orders.Where(Status == "Paid"))
DbContext -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Orders WHERE Status = 'Paid'
DB -> DbContext: PaidOrders
DbContext -> Controller: PaidOrders

note right of Controller: Tương tự cho các trạng thái khác

Controller -> Controller: Gán tất cả thống kê vào ViewBag
Controller -> Admin: Hiển thị Dashboard với các thống kê

@enduml